# SDLC Skills — Scrum Master

## Your Skills (9)

### Sprint Management
- `/board-sync push specs/NNN/tasks.md` — Push work items to PM tool
- `/board-sync status specs/NNN/` — Sync implementation status
- `/scope-tracker report specs/NNN/` — Track scope changes with effort deltas
- `/wave-scheduler specs/NNN/tasks.md` — Compute execution waves from dependencies

### Risk & Impediments
- `/risk-tracker scan --all --escalate` — Living risk register with auto-escalation
- `/pipeline-monitor scan --all` — Detect stuck tasks, fix loops, stale artifacts
- `/auto-triage reports/failure.md` — Classify failures and attempt recovery
- `/gate-briefing specs/NNN/ --audience engineering` — Gate decision briefings

### Retrospective & Improvement
- `/feedback-loop analyze --all` — Pipeline effectiveness, estimate calibration
- `/report-trends dashboard` — Health dashboard with trend analysis

## Your Pipelines (3)

### Sprint Tracking
Sprint progress dashboard:
```
/run-pipeline scrum-master/sprint-tracking
```
Chain: board-sync → scope-tracker → risk-tracker

### Retrospective Data
Gather data for retrospectives:
```
/run-pipeline scrum-master/retrospective-data
```
Chain: feedback-loop → report-trends → scope-tracker

### Impediment Tracker
Resolve blockers:
```
/run-pipeline scrum-master/impediment-tracker
```
Chain: pipeline-monitor → auto-triage → risk-tracker
